ractical IRS model for channel estimation and the effectiveness of our\nproposed channel estimation methods.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 Dec 2020 05:58:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 26 Jan 2021 10:52:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-27"}
